{"type":"message","id":"5cf8e4c7","parentId":"3d0a1deb","timestamp":"2026-04-27T17:04:38.687Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now check the iCloud emails. The ones shown seem to be older (from Jan, Apr 13). Let me read them to see if there are any new ones from today. The IDs 8, 7, 6 are listed but have R flag (read). Let me check if there are any unread ones from today or recent. Let me read the most recent one to get details.\n\nActually, looking at the output:\n- ID 8: RC Leasing - \"Re: Looking for new apartment\" - 2026-04-27 12:20 (today!)\n- ID 7: RC Leasing - \"Re: Looking for new apartment\" - 2026-04-13 (older)\n- ID 6: Taylor Alexander - \"Re: Apartment Inquiry (Around mid June)\" - 2026-01-22 (old)\n\n\nThese appear to be read messages already, so I should check for any unread ones from today.\n","thinkingSignature":"e8de3632a5786c4bf5c924d88f942823f509535d3b5a555784163ad7772a2d13"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_proqa6bj76tl_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"himalaya envelope list --account icloud 2>&1 | grep -v WARN | grep -v \" R \""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":115,"output":244,"cacheRead":19968,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20327,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777309474258,"responseId":"063eca2284fb77e4ae1e6cd412d22d14"}}
