{"type":"message","id":"e2f78dc1","parentId":"0d221274","timestamp":"2026-04-27T17:04:43.189Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The R flag means read, and ! means flagged. So only id 8 is flagged (unread) today. Let me read it. The others are from mid-April and January, so likely not \"new in the last hour.\" Let me just read id 8 since it's from today and unread.","thinkingSignature":"968a1f0168b87d012a7ab587ac45305124fd258c48c5cc7ab0806ffebc3a568f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_f0m6bifvoxsm_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"himalaya message read 8 --account icloud 2>&1 | grep -v WARN | head -50"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":204,"output":110,"cacheRead":20160,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20474,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777309481463,"responseId":"063eca29c2fd4a826821815abea17b6c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0f38301a","parentId":"e2f78dc1","timestamp":"2026-04-27T17:04:44.114Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_f0m6bifvoxsm_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"From: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nGood Morning,\n\nOnce Logan completes his, I can run the apps. When are you looking to move by so I can make sure I will have one Available?\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Saturday, April 25, 2026 1:49 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nHi Amy, I wanted to reach out to let you know that I have completed and submitted my portion of the rental application for Royal Cove. I am currently waiting on my partner, Logan, to finish his part o\nReport This Email<removed-link>\n\n\nHi Amy,\n\n\n\nI wanted to reach out to let you know that I have completed and submitted my portion of the rental application for Royal Cove. I am currently waiting on my partner, Logan, to finish his part of the application on his end.\n\n\n\nWe are still very interested in a 1 bedroom / 1 bathroom unit. Please let me know if you need anything else from me in the meantime, or if there are any updates on availability.\n\n\n\nThank you,\n\nRobert Galletta\n<#part type=image/png filename=\"/Users/bobbygalletta/Downloads/Outlook-A picture .png\"><#/part>"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":915,"aggregated":"From: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nGood Morning,\n\nOnce Logan completes his, I can run the apps. When are you looking to move by so I can make sure I will have one Available?\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Saturday, April 25, 2026 1:49 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nHi Amy, I wanted to reach out to let you know that I have completed and submitted my portion of the rental application for Royal Cove. I am currently waiting on my partner, Logan, to finish his part o\nReport This Email<removed-link>\n\n\nHi Amy,\n\n\n\nI wanted to reach out to let you know that I have completed and submitted my portion of the rental application for Royal Cove. I am currently waiting on my partner, Logan, to finish his part of the application on his end.\n\n\n\nWe are still very interested in a 1 bedroom / 1 bathroom unit. Please let me know if you need anything else from me in the meantime, or if there are any updates on availability.\n\n\n\nThank you,\n\nRobert Galletta\n<#part type=image/png filename=\"/Users/bobbygalletta/Downloads/Outlook-A picture .png\"><#/part>","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777309484114}}
{"type":"message","id":"b61beeaa","parentId":"0f38301a","timestamp":"2026-04-27T17:04:47.387Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the iCloud situation. All 3 emails are marked as \"R\" (read), but the most recent one (id 8, dated today 12:20 UTC) is also marked \"!\" which typically means recent/new. Let me check if these are actually new within the last hour.\n\nActually, looking at the flags:\n- `!` = flagged/important\n- `R` = read\n\nSo all three are read emails. The `!` on id 8 might just mean flagged, not unread. But the date shows today at 12:20+00:00 which is about 4 hours ago, not within the last hour.\n\nWait, the cron is set to check \"newer_than:1h\" for Gmail. \n\nFor iCloud, there's no built-in time filter like Gmail's, so these messages are all older than the 1-hour window—they're from today at 12:20, 2 weeks ago, and January. None of them actually qualify as new messages I should act on. I should send the iCloud summary since Bobby asked for it anyway, noting the recent apartment inquiry from RC Leasing with the flag indicating they can proceed once Logan completes his application.","thinkingSignature":"aa9d45474ef636cb71eb563e3b85d5d7d478ace9938d38ffec0b585b3c7739b5"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xd45ti3stj6e_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"telegram","message":"📬 ICLOUD — No new emails (last 1hr)\n\n💬 SEEN TODAY:\n• RC Leasing — Re: Looking for new apartment\n  └ Ready to run apps once Logan completes his application — when are you looking to move by?","target":"8212808444"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":452,"output":359,"cacheRead":20352,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21163,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777309484117,"responseId":"063eca2c689d5e8674bf543f4830e8a3"}}
