{"type":"message","id":"6c2877a9","parentId":"51fe7c65","timestamp":"2026-04-27T17:04:49.344Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both emails sent. Gmail had no new emails in the last hour, and iCloud had no new unread emails - just one seen today from RC Leasing about the apartment application. All done!\n","thinkingSignature":"4d57e6f1dea55326753826dc79548c925cf558cb936f1a845bbe3c1f499bc9f8"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nBoth messages sent. Summary:\n\n- **Gmail:** No new emails in the last hour\n- **iCloud:** No new unread emails — but there's a seen message from RC Leasing about the Royal Cove apartment application. They're waiting on Logan to finish his portion and asking when you're looking to move by. ⚠️"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":152,"output":107,"cacheRead":20800,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21059,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777309487771,"responseId":"063eca2f84c694448ba6ba22250d514a"}}
